    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/98b76575beca9b1090696018686b0d22.poster.avif?t=1762177807\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/98b76575beca9b1090696018686b0d22.webm?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/98b76575beca9b1090696018686b0d22.mp4?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Astral Break is a fusion of mech and roguelite action. Customize your mech, from modular body parts to software configurations. Fight and evolve your mech throughout the battle. Terminated? Unlock more upgrades with battle data to refine and perfect your build!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/bc9b3e2853e2c5155004a08d2941f581.poster.avif?t=1762177807\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/bc9b3e2853e2c5155004a08d2941f581.webm?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/bc9b3e2853e2c5155004a08d2941f581.mp4?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/bf70ca4d086dac1877e05d16caf625a5.poster.avif?t=1762177807\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/bf70ca4d086dac1877e05d16caf625a5.webm?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/bf70ca4d086dac1877e05d16caf625a5.mp4?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/16bf2f56cb7832413ed45f08fb67ec02.poster.avif?t=1762177807\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/16bf2f56cb7832413ed45f08fb67ec02.webm?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense Combat</strong> - Thrilling thrust controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Building</strong> - Collect, upgrade &amp; customize modular body parts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Character</strong> - 6 playable characters, each with unique mechanics &amp; skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Non-stop Action</strong> - Action packed procedural dungeon crawler</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power</strong> - Dynamic powerups &amp; equipment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Synergy</strong> - Mix &amp; match characters, modular body parts, powerups &amp; equipment</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/4adce8c3c3f418e8255f9971829624ce.poster.avif?t=1762177807\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extras/4adce8c3c3f418e8255f9971829624ce.webm?t=1762177807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145570/extr